AMENDEDANALYSIS
This bill allows the insurance commissioner to hold an informational public hearing when a health
carrier ends a provider contract affecting 1,000 or more patients; requires continued access to the
provider for a limited period; requires written notice of the contract termination; and authorizes the
insurancedepartmenttoadoptrulesregardingnoticeofterminationofprovidercontracts.
